NSContactsUsageDescription: Contacts access allows you to set up reminders to notify you when messaging specific people.
NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription: Photo library access allows you to attach photos to reminders.
NSCameraUsageDescription: Camera access allows you to take photos to attach to reminders.
NSPhotoLibraryAddUsageDescription: Photo library write access allows you to add photos taken within Reminders to your photo library.
NSLocationUsageDescription: Location access allows you to set up reminders to notify you when you arrive at or leave a specific place.
NSSiriUsageDescription: Allow Siri to make suggestions in Reminders and learn from how you use Reminders to make suggestions across apps.
